  "body": "I segmented these into P0, P1, P2. [RH]\n\nP0\n\n* [x] ISSUE #9342\n**Error message copy needs to be changed**\n* [x] ISSUE #9345\n**\"More\" button behavior is wrong**\n\n* [x] ISSUE #9350\n**Change `Cancel` to `<` and remove extra screen if only one key**\n* [x] ISSUE #9354 \n**Don't ask for the Keycard all the time to sign in**\n\nP1\n\n* [ ] ISSUE #9349\n**\"Wrong passcode\" indicator**\n* [ ] ISSUE #9346\n**Replace ... characters in address with the horizontal ellipsis special character**\n* [ ] ISSUE #9347\n**Show the number of passcode wrong attempts**\n* [ ] ISSUE #9341\n**Active state of pinpad buttons**\n* [ ] ISSUE #9353\n**Layout fixes and support of small screens**\n* [ ] ISSUE #9344\n**\"Access key\" copy, layout and behavior** - fix copy p0, responsiveness & drop down are p1 [RH]\n\nP2\n\n* [ ] ISSUE #9316 (Low priority, WIP)\n**Review of card errors depending on their state**\n* [ ] ISSUE #9348 \n**Frozen keys** - Is this a new feature idea or was it planned? [RH]\n\n",
